## config

Host *
  ForwardX11 no
  ForwardX11Trusted no
  ForwardAgent no
  TCPKeepAlive yes
  ServerAliveInterval 15
  ServerAliveCountMax 30
  GlobalKnownHostsFile /dev/null
  UserKnownHostsFile /dev/null
  StrictHostKeyChecking no
  LogLevel ERROR

Host github.com
  Hostname github.com
  User git
  PreferredAuthentications publickey
